query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 t1 tq1 u1) NoHashJoin(a1 q1 t1 tq1 u1 s) NoHashJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1 b) */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('adobe-illustrator',
'formulas',
'functions',
'posts',
'theme-development',
'wp-query')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('academia',
'graphicdesign',
'scifi',
'webapps',
'wordpress')
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name ilike '%outs%'
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id;
